title: Grateful Dead - Dick's Picks Vol 15 1977-09-03 Englishtown [FLAC
description:
This one is special because I was there.

Dick's Picks Volume 15 is the 15th live album in the Dick's Picks series of releases by the Grateful Dead. It was recorded on September 3, 1977 at the Raceway Park in Englishtown, New Jersey. Also appearing at the event were the New Riders of the Purple Sage and the Marshall Tucker Band.
